text: Nathalie Lemmens (born ) is a Belgian female volleyball player. She is part of the Belgium women's national volleyball team. She competed at the 2015 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix, 2017 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix, and 2018 FIVB Volleyball Women's Nations League.
